                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[19.06.2009]</p>
                <p>The Ministers of Justice of the Council of Europe member countries undertook today to adopt definite measures to combat domestic violence and break the silence surrounding it. 
</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/jd/whats-new/News/2009/twelve-council-of-europe-member-states-s.html?id=568009" class="ISI_IGNORE">
