            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/jd/whats-new/News/2009/twelve-council-of-europe-member-states-s.html?id=568009" title="">
                        Twelve Council of Europe member states sign the Convention on Access to Official Documents
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.06.2009]</p>
                <p>At the Council of Europe Conference of Ministers of Justice in Tromsø, twelve member states signed the Convention on Access to Official Documents, the first binding international legal instrument laying down a general right of access to official documents.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
