                        Opening speech - Breaking the silence
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.06.2009]</p>
                <p>The Council of Europe Conference of Ministers of Justice began in Tromsø Thursday 18 June 2009. Knut Storberget, Norwegian Minister of Justice and the Police, gave the opening address.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
