            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/jd/press-center/pressemeldinger/2009/childrens-houses-help-children.html?id=567646" title="">
                        Children’s houses help children
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[17.06.2009]</p>
                <p>A year and a half after the first children’s house was established in Norway, almost 700 children who have been exposed or subjected to abuse have received assistance, care and treatment at children’s houses nationwide. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
