            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/jd/whats-new/News/2009/storberget-visits-malawi.html?id=556000" title="">
                        Storberget visits Malawi
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[24.11.2009]</p>
                <p>How to mobilize African men to change the African men? Abusive men and the relationship between substance abuse and domestic violence is on the agenda when Minister of Justice Knut Storberget visits Malawi from 21 to 26 April. "I look forward to learning more about how Malawi is dealing with these issues," said Storberget.
</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
