            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/jd/press-center/pressemeldinger/2009/government-commitment-to-svalbard.html?id=555716" title="">
                        Government commitment to Svalbard
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[22.04.2009]</p>
                <p>The Government will preserve Svalbard’s unique natural wilderness and develop the archipelago as a platform for climate research. At the same time, the Government will continue to develop a robust family community in Longyearbyen, continue coal mining and further develop tourism within the framework of strict environmental standards. These are some of the main points of Report No. 22 (2008-2009) to the Storting, Svalbard.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
