                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/jd/whats-new/News/2008/criminanlizing-the-purchase-of-sexual-ac.html?id=537854" title="">
                        Criminalizing the purchase of sexual activity
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[01.12.2008]</p>
                <p>In November 2008, the Norwegian Parliament voted for changes in the legislation on prostitution, in effect criminalizing the purchase of sexual activity or a sexual act, by introducing a new section 202a in the General Civil Penal Code</p>
                
                
